    {
        question: "What kind of support and Customer Success do enterprise software and services teams get?",
        answer: "Enterprise plans include 24x7 support, a dedicated Slack channel with the engineering team, a Customer Success Program staffed with implementation experts, and a clear escalation path for production issues. Quarterly business reviews, joint roadmap discussions, and named contacts for upgrades and migrations. The cadence software vendors and consultancies expect from a platform their delivery teams depend on.",
    },
    {
        question: "How does Kestra compare to Temporal or Camunda for embedding in a software product?",
        answer: `<a href="/vs/temporal">Temporal</a> requires code-first Java/Go/TypeScript workers and has no no-code UI for business users. <a href="/vs/camunda">Camunda</a> is BPMN-centric with significant modeling overhead. Kestra ships as a single deployable unit with a declarative YAML engine, REST API, a self-service App UI for non-engineers, and a Terraform provider for fleet deployment. Software vendors embed Kestra as the orchestration backbone in their product and expose Kestra Apps to customers as the self-service workflow UI — no orchestration expertise required from end users.`,
    },
    {
        question: "What is the best workflow orchestration platform for multi-tenant SaaS products?",
        answer: "Kestra's namespace isolation maps directly to SaaS tenancy — each customer or workspace owns their namespace, flows, secrets, and execution history. One control plane serves hundreds of tenants with namespace-level RBAC, per-tenant audit logs, and dedicated worker groups for performance isolation. The Terraform provider deploys and manages namespaces at fleet scale. Software vendors use Kestra to power the automation layer inside their SaaS product without building orchestration infrastructure from scratch.",
    },
    {
        question: "How do consulting and managed-service firms use Kestra for client delivery?",
        answer: "Consulting and MSP teams use Kestra to standardize delivery across client engagements. One shared control plane with namespace isolation separates client environments, secrets, and workflows. Git-backed YAML flows travel with the engagement — no configuration drift between environments. The Terraform provider deploys standard namespace templates at the start of each engagement, cutting setup time from days to minutes.",
    },
]

---

<Layout {title} {description} headerTheme="lightText">
    <SchemaFAQ items={FAQ} slot="head" />
    <SchemaService
        slot="head"
        serviceType="Workflow Orchestration for Software and Managed Service Providers"
        audienceType="SaaS Companies, Software Vendors, Consulting Firms, and Managed Service Providers"
        description={description}
    />
    <div class="software-providers">

        <section class="hero">
            <img src="/hero-grid.svg" alt="" class="hero-bg-grid" aria-hidden="true" />
            <div class="hero-inner">
                <div class="badge-pill" data-usal="zoomin">
                    <Icon name="mdi:application-cog-outline" />
                    <span>Software, Consulting &amp; Service Providers</span>
                </div>

                <h1 data-usal="fade-u">
                    Workflow orchestration for<br />
                    <span class="gradient">software providers and consulting firms.</span>
                </h1>

                <p class="subtitle" data-usal="fade-l">
                    Onboard customers, ship environments, and run multi-tenant workloads on the platform your delivery team already wants.
                    Build it once, deliver it identically the next fifty times. Replace the brittle automation between your product and your customers.
                </p>

                <div class="tags" data-usal="fade-l">
                    {HERO_TAGS.map((tag) => (
                        <span class="tag">
                            <Icon name={tag.icon} class="tag-icon" />
                            {tag.label}
                        </span>
                    ))}
                </div>

                <div class="exec-panel-wrapper" data-usal="fade-up">
                    <div class="exec-panel">
                        <div class="exec-panel__header">
                            <span class="exec-panel__dot"></span>
                            <span class="exec-panel__title">onboard-tenant</span>
                            <span class="exec-panel__meta">namespace · company.delivery.tenants</span>
                            <span class="exec-panel__duration">4.2s</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="exec-panel__body">
                            <div class="exec-row">
                                <span class="exec-row__check">✓</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__name">provision_infra</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__type">terraform.cli.TerraformCLI</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__result">12 resources</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="exec-row">
                                <span class="exec-row__check">✓</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__name">deploy_default_flows</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__type">core.flow.Subflow</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__result">4 flows</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="exec-row">
                                <span class="exec-row__check">✓</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__name">seed_baseline_data</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__type">jdbc.postgresql.Query</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__result">250 rows</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="exec-row">
                                <span class="exec-row__check">✓</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__name">install_app_stack</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__type">kubernetes.PodCreate</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__result">ready</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="exec-row">
                                <span class="exec-row__check">✓</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__name">run_validation</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__type">core.flow.Parallel</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__result">8 checks</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="exec-row">
                                <span class="exec-row__check">✓</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__name">notify_cs</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__type">notifications.slack</span>
                                <span class="exec-row__result">sent</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="exec-panel__footer">
                            <span class="exec-footer__item">Multi-tenant</span>
                            <span class="exec-footer__sep">·</span>
                            <span class="exec-footer__item">GitOps-native</span>
                            <span class="exec-footer__sep">·</span>
                            <span class="exec-footer__item">Audit-ready</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="hero-ctas" data-usal="zoomin">
                    <Link href="/demo" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Book a Demo</Link>
                </div>

                <div class="hero-logos" data-usal="fade-u">
                    <span class="hero-logos__label">Trusted by software vendors, SaaS platforms, consultancies &amp; managed-service providers</span>
                    <div class="hero-logos__row">
                        <a href="/customers/amdocs" aria-label="Read the Amdocs customer story">
                            <Image src={AmdocsLogoImg} alt="Amdocs" class="hero-logos__item hero-logos__item--amdocs" />
                        </a>
                        <Image src={AcxiomLogoImg} alt="Acxiom" class="hero-logos__item hero-logos__item--acxiom" />
                        <Image src={KPMGLogoImg} alt="KPMG" class="hero-logos__item hero-logos__item--kpmg" />
                        <Image src={HCLLogoImg} alt="HCL" class="hero-logos__item hero-logos__item--hcl" />
                        <a href="/customers/sopht" aria-label="Read the Sopht customer story">
                            <Image src={SophtLogoImg} alt="Sopht" class="hero-logos__item hero-logos__item--sopht" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="flow">
            <div class="container-xxl">
                <h2 class="flow__title text-center">
                    How <span class="highlight">multi-tenant workflow orchestration</span> powers SaaS, consulting, and MSP delivery.
                </h2>
                <p class="flow__lead">
                    Customer onboarding. Environment-as-a-Service. Multi-tenant data pipelines. AI in your product.
                    Whether you're shipping a SaaS, running a managed service, or delivering for a client,
                    the engine is the same. Cloud, self-hosted, or air-gapped. Multi-tenant by namespace. Audit-ready by default.
                </p>

                <div class="flow__grid">
                    <div class="flow__steps">
                        {FLOW_STAGES.map((stage, idx) => (
                            <div class={`flow-block flow-${idx}`}>
                                <div class="flow-block__content">
                                    <span class={`flow-block__label label-${stage.id}`}>{stage.label}</span>
                                    <div class={`flow-block__card card-${stage.id}`}>
                                        <div class="flow-block__items">
                                            {stage.items.map(item => (
                                                <div class="flow-block__item">{item}</div>
                                            ))}
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                {idx < FLOW_STAGES.length - 1 && (
                                    <div class={`flow-arrow arrow-${idx}`}>
                                        <div class="line" />
                                        <Icon name="mdi:play" class="head" width={16} height={16} />
                                    </div>
                                )}
                            </div>
                        ))}
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h5 class="flow__footer text-center">
                    Each step is a declarative YAML task. Wrap a brittle Python wrapper today. Replace it with a flow tomorrow. Build it once, deliver it identically across every client.
                </h5>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="workloads">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="workloads__head">
                    <h2>Workflow orchestration use cases for SaaS products, consulting delivery, and managed services.</h2>
                    <p>Twelve concrete patterns, from onboarding the next customer to retiring the brittle Python holding your platform together. Build each one once. Run it across every tenant, every environment, every client. Replayable per execution, audit-ready by default.</p>
                </div>
                {WORKLOAD_CATEGORIES.map(cat => (
                    <div class="workloads__group">
                        <h3 class="workloads__category">{cat.name}</h3>
                        <div class="workloads__grid">
                            {cat.items.map(item => (
                                <div class="workload-card">
                                    <Icon name={item.icon} class="workload-card__icon" />
                                    <h4 class="workload-card__title">{item.title}</h4>
                                    <p class="workload-card__desc">{item.description}</p>
                                </div>
                            ))}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                ))}
            </div>
        </section>

        <Quotes {quotes} client:load />

        <section class="enterprise surface-inverse">
            <div class="container-xxl">
                <h2 class="enterprise__title" data-usal="fade-r">
                    SaaS orchestration requirements: <span class="highlight">multi-tenant isolation, Terraform, and embedding</span>.
                </h2>
                <NoGapGrid items={ENTERPRISE_FEATURES}>
                    <div class="feature-card feature-card--cta">
                        <a href="/demo" class="btn btn-secondary" data-usal="zoomin">
                            Book a Demo
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </NoGapGrid>
            </div>
        </section>

        <BlueprintTabs
            title={`SaaS and MSP workflow orchestration <span class="highlight">examples and blueprints</span>.`}
            lead="Real workflows running today inside SaaS platforms, consultancies, and managed-service teams. Copy the YAML, adapt to your stack, deploy through your existing CI and approvals."
            items={BUILD_TABS.map((t) => ({ ...t, plugins: t.plugins.map((p) => p.cls) }))}
        />

        <GoFurther />

        <PluginsBlock>
            <Fragment slot="title">
                Integrates with the <span class="highlight">stack software and services teams</span> already run.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="description">
                Native plugins for AWS, GCP, Azure, Kubernetes, Docker, Terraform, Ansible, Argo CD, Salesforce,
                HubSpot, Snowflake, Databricks, dbt, Postgres, Kafka, ServiceNow, Vault, Splunk, OpenLineage,
                plus 1,200+ more. Or build the exact integration your product or your customer needs.
            </Fragment>
        </PluginsBlock>

        <SeeHow cta={{ text: "Book a Demo", href: "/demo" }}>
            <Fragment slot="title">Ship every customer, every product, every delivery on the same engine.</Fragment>
            One control plane for onboarding, environments, multi-tenant pipelines, and AI workflows.
            Cloud, self-hosted, or air-gapped. Build it once, deliver it identically the next fifty times,
            and prove the audit on demand.
        </SeeHow>

        <Faq items={FAQ} client:visible />
    </div>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
    // ── Software & Services palette: deep magenta ────────────────────
    // Distinct from FSI (yellow), Healthcare (green), Automotive (red),
    // Retail (violet), Public Services (cobalt blue). Reads as modern
    // builder / SaaS / craft.
    $sw-magenta:        #DB2777;
    $sw-magenta-bright: #F472B6;
    $sw-magenta-light:  #F9A8D4;
    $sw-magenta-deep:   #831843;
    $sw-platinum:       #F4E8EE;

    .software-providers { overflow: clip; }

    :global(html.dark) .software-providers {
        .flow,
        .workloads,
        .enterprise {
            background: #1C1C20;
        }
        :global(section.quotes-wrapper),
        :global(section.plugin-block),
        :global(.see),
        :global(.blueprint-tabs) {
            background: #1C1C20;
        }
    }

    :global(.blueprint-tabs h2 .highlight) {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #{$sw-magenta}, #{$sw-magenta-bright});
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .hero {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: #0d0612;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: calc(-1 * var(--top-bar-height, 67px) - var(--announce-height, 0px));
        padding: calc(var(--top-bar-height, 67px) + var(--announce-height, 0px) + 5rem) 1.5rem 6rem;

        @include media-breakpoint-down(md) {
            padding: calc(var(--top-bar-height, 67px) + var(--announce-height, 0px) + 3rem) 1rem 4rem;
        }

        &::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -260px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 1100px;
            height: 520px;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.32) 0%, rgba(219, 39, 119, 0) 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }
    }

    .hero-bg-grid {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1720px;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        object-position: center top;
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 0;
        opacity: 0.5;
    }

    .hero-inner {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2rem;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 68rem;
        color: $white;
        text-align: center;

        @include media-breakpoint-down(md) { gap: 1.5rem; }

        h1 {
            color: $white;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #{$sw-magenta-bright}, #{$sw-magenta-light});
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
            font-size: $font-size-lg;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 48rem;
            margin: 0;

            @include media-breakpoint-down(md) { font-size: $font-size-md; }
        }
    }

    .badge-pill {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        width: fit-content;
        padding: 4px 1.125rem;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        border-radius: 2.5rem;
        background: #0d0612;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        font-size: $font-size-xs;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: $sw-magenta-bright;

        &::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            border-radius: 2.5rem;
            padding: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #{$sw-magenta} 0%, #{$sw-magenta-light} 100%);
            -webkit-mask: linear-gradient($white 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient($white 0 0);
            -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
            mask-composite: exclude;
            z-index: -1;
        }
    }

    .tags {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 8px;
    }

    .tag {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        padding: 6px 14px;
        border-radius: 9999px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
        font-size: $font-size-xs;
        white-space: nowrap;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;

        &:hover {
            border-color: rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.55);
            background: rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.14);
            color: $white;

            :global(.tag-icon) { color: $sw-magenta-light; }
        }

        :global(.tag-icon) {
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            color: $sw-magenta-bright;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
    }

    @property --sw-neon-angle {
        syntax: '<angle>';
        inherits: false;
        initial-value: 0deg;
    }

    @keyframes sw-neon-trace {
        to { --sw-neon-angle: 360deg; }
    }

    .exec-panel-wrapper {
        --sw-neon-angle: 0deg;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: conic-gradient(
            from var(--sw-neon-angle),
            rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.16) 0deg,
            rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.16) 320deg,
            #{$sw-magenta}            340deg,
            $sw-platinum              350deg,
            #{$sw-magenta}            360deg
        );
        padding: 1px;
        box-shadow:
            0 1.214px 10.321px 0 rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.28) inset,
            -6.667px -7.143px 31.334px 3.333px rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.6);
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 640px;
        animation: sw-neon-trace 5s linear infinite;
    }

    .exec-panel {
        background: #120712;
        border-radius: 9px;
        overflow: hidden;
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        text-align: left;

        &__header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            background: rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.08);
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            font-family: $font-family-monospace;
            font-size: $font-size-xs;
        }

        &__dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: $sw-magenta-bright;
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px $sw-magenta-bright;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        &__title {
            color: $white;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        &__meta {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
            flex: 1;

            @include media-breakpoint-down(sm) { display: none; }
        }

        &__duration {
            color: $sw-magenta-light;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        &__body {
            padding: 14px 16px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        &__footer {
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            background: rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.06);
            font-family: $font-family-monospace;
            font-size: $font-size-xs;
            color: $sw-magenta-light;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .exec-footer__sep { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25); }
    }

    .exec-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 20px minmax(130px, 1fr) minmax(150px, 1fr) minmax(90px, auto);
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        padding: 6px 8px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-family: $font-family-monospace;
        font-size: $font-size-xs;
        transition: background 0.2s;

        &:hover { background: rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.10); }

        @include media-breakpoint-down(sm) {
            grid-template-columns: 20px 1fr auto;
        }

        &__check {
            color: $sw-magenta-bright;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        &__name {
            color: $white;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        &__type {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);

            @include media-breakpoint-down(sm) { display: none; }
        }

        &__result {
            color: $sw-magenta-light;
            text-align: right;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
    }

    .hero-ctas {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;

        .btn {
            justify-content: center;

            @include media-breakpoint-down(md) {
                width: auto;
                min-width: 200px;
            }
        }
    }

    // ── Hero logo strip ──────────────────────────────────────────────
    // 5 logos on a single row at md+, normalised to the same optical
    // weight via per-logo max-height + max-width tuned to each SVG's
    // aspect ratio. Sizing system matches the other industry pages.
    .hero-logos {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        padding-top: 2rem;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 60rem;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        text-align: center;

        &__label {
            font-size: $font-size-xs;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.14em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        }

        &__row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
            align-items: center;
            justify-items: center;
            column-gap: 2rem;
            row-gap: 1.5rem;
            width: 100%;

            @include media-breakpoint-down(md) {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                column-gap: 1.5rem;
                row-gap: 1.75rem;
            }
        }

        &__item {
            width: auto;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
            opacity: 0.85;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
            object-fit: contain;
            max-width: 100%;

            &:hover { opacity: 1; }

            // Unified optical sizing across all industry pages:
            // text wordmarks 36px, small text 32px, compact icon+text
            // 42px, stacked icon+text 52-56px.
            &--amdocs { max-height: 32px; max-width: 150px; }   // small text
            &--acxiom { max-height: 36px; max-width: 160px; }   // text wordmark
            &--kpmg   { max-height: 36px; max-width: 130px; }   // text wordmark
            &--hcl    { max-height: 36px; max-width: 130px; }   // text wordmark
            &--sopht  { max-height: 42px; max-width: 150px; }   // compact icon + text

            @include media-breakpoint-down(md) {
                &--amdocs { max-height: 36px; max-width: 170px; }
                &--acxiom { max-height: 40px; max-width: 180px; }
                &--kpmg   { max-height: 40px; max-width: 150px; }
                &--hcl    { max-height: 40px; max-width: 150px; }
                &--sopht  { max-height: 48px; max-width: 170px; }
            }
        }
    }

    $stages: (
        "trigger": ( "bg": #fff3d3, "border": #a87f4f, "label": #b87f00 ),
        "ingest":  ( "bg": #cbe2ff, "border": #6b62f2, "label": #0069c6 ),
        "process": ( "bg": #e3cffe, "border": #bb62f2, "label": #822bfd ),
        "act":     ( "bg": #d3ffe0, "border": #4fa876, "label": #007336 )
    );

    .flow {
        position: relative;
        background: var(--ks-background-secondary);
        padding: 5.5rem 1rem;
        overflow: hidden;

        .container-xxl {
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        &__title {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--ks-content-primary);

            .highlight {
                background: linear-gradient(90deg, #{$sw-magenta}, #{$sw-magenta-bright});
                -webkit-background-clip: text;
                -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
                background-clip: text;
            }
        }

